*Aerodrom* je počeo prihvatati putnike pre tri godine. (The airport started receiving passengers three years ago.)

Putnici čekaju na *aerodromu* da otplešu svoju destinaciju. (The passengers are waiting at the airport to depart to their destination.)

*Aerodromu* su pridružili nove kompanije za avio prevoz. (New airline companies joined the airport.)

Grad je pre tri godine dobio novi *aerodrom*. (The city got a new airport three years ago.)

*Aerodrom* je uspostavio nove letove za destinacije širom sveta. (The airport established new flights to destinations around the world.)